urls.description: What should I do if Points are not credited to my account? Members may submit a missing mile claim within 6 months (180 days) from the date of travel. First, log in to the Enri ch site, then complete the relevant form under “Claim Missing Enrich Points”. Be sure to retain your original travel documents (i.e. boarding passes and ticket stubs) and partner receipts (i.e. hotel receipts, copy of car rental agreement, invoices/ receipts/ statements from other Partners) as you will need this to complete the
